{
  "id": "tpl_demo_prreview_001",
  "name": "pr_review_workflow",
  "display_name": "PR 自动审查工作流",
  "description": "演示 PR 审查技能，自动化执行代码审查、安全检查和质量分析",
  "icon": "📋",
  "category": "testing",
  "subcategory": "code-review",
  "tags": ["pr", "review", "code-review", "github", "demo", "skill"],
  "project_type": "workflow",
  "prompt_template": "请帮我创建一个 PR 审查工作流：\n\n**PR 编号/URL：** {{prTarget}}\n**审查重点：** {{reviewFocus}}\n**审查严格度：** {{strictLevel}}\n\n**工作流步骤：**\n\n### 步骤1：获取 PR 信息\n```\n/pr-reviewer review {{prTarget}}\n```\n\n### 步骤2：代码质量分析\n```\n/code-review {{prTarget}}\n```\n\n{{#eq reviewFocus \"安全审查\"}}\n### 步骤3：安全漏洞扫描\n```\n/security-audit {{prTarget}}\n```\n{{/eq}}\n\n### 步骤4：生成审查报告\n综合所有检查结果，生成结构化审查报告。\n\n### 步骤5：保存审查记录\n```\n/memory-management save \"PR审查完成: {{prTarget}}\"\n```\n\n**使用的技能：** pr-reviewer, code-review, memory-management",
  "variables_schema": [
    {
      "name": "prTarget",
      "label": "PR 目标",
      "type": "string",
      "required": true,
      "placeholder": "#123 或 https://github.com/org/repo/pull/123"
    },
    {
      "name": "reviewFocus",
      "label": "审查重点",
      "type": "select",
      "required": true,
      "options": [
        { "value": "代码质量", "label": "代码质量" },
        { "value": "安全审查", "label": "安全审查" },
        { "value": "性能审查", "label": "性能审查" },
        { "value": "全面审查", "label": "全面审查" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "strictLevel",
      "label": "严格度",
      "type": "select",
      "required": false,
      "default": "standard",
      "options": [
        { "value": "relaxed", "label": "宽松" },
        { "value": "standard", "label": "标准" },
        { "value": "strict", "label": "严格" }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "file_structure": {},
  "default_files": [],
  "is_builtin": true,
  "author": "ChainlessChain Team",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "usage_count": 0,
  "rating": 0,
  "rating_count": 0,
  "skills_used": ["pr-reviewer", "code-review", "memory-management"],
  "difficulty": "intermediate",
  "execution_engine": "skill"
}
